  <description type="morphology">Plants 1–2 m, rhizomes extensive.  Leaves: petiole 3–6 mm; blade 2–8(–10) × (0.5–)1.2–4.5 cm, base cuneate to rounded, apex acute, apiculate, rounded, or retuse.  Pedicels: bracteoles absent.  Flowers fragrant; sepal lobes triangular; corolla 6.5–10 mm; nectariferous disc 10-lobed; ovary 5-lobed.  Capsules erect, 3.2–5 × 4.8–6.5 mm.  Seeds ca. 1 × 0.5 mm, not winged.  2n = ca. 66.</description>
